SKILL RESCUE

General Description:
  Attempt to be heroic by rescuing a person who is being attacked and letting
  the monster who is attacking to attack you instead.

Chance of Success:
  If your rescue skill exceeds random(1,101), then you succeed in the rescue.

Results of Success:
  Whoever you rescue stops fighting the monster, you start fighting the monster
  and the monster starts fighting you.

  You may not type a command for 2 rounds after a successful rescue.

Results of Failure:
  Nothing.

Restrictions:
  If you are being attacked by more than 2 creatures you may not rescue anyone.

